Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是為了王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一連串的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並非星靈們的純粹願望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是星靈王？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道連星靈王都發生了什麼變化嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一切難道不是星靈王設下的局嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這是真的 那麼要做的只有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把星靈王打飛 結束這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們做得到嗎 人類
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.38,0:00:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星靈王由我來守護
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我乃蛇夫座的奧芬克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潛藏於星靈王陰影之下的第十三名星靈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要小看滅龍魔法師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:01:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全天88星座 閃耀 星圖史話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等的就是這一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等著你們拚命地將星靈強制關門
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來 所有的12星座就都回到了星靈王那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天球儀發出的紅光 會通過星座到達星靈王那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這從一開始 就是為了將強大的力量聚集到星靈王之處的儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自由儀式·選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偉大的星靈王因為成為了日蝕星靈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以發揮強大的力量 而且在追求此上更強的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃道12門的星靈們畏懼這份力量 想要從星靈界逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:02:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,12天的自由 也就是僅有12天的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我將此視為讓星靈王得到更強力量的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星靈王竟然在暴走…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們想要守護星靈 結果卻將他們逼上了絕路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.53,0:02:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果將想要逃脫的星靈 送回了星靈王暴走的星靈界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並不僅僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化作日蝕星靈的星靈王只要積蓄力量 持續暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星靈界就會越來越崩壞 最終消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可笑了 你來幾次都一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:38.13,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(640,450)\fad(524,0}星靈獸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:04:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天球儀…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅色的光消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 臭蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要小看我們妖精的尾巴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然衝著笛子來 真是太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 夏 黃道十二門的星座正在消失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主 您沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星座消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣洛基他們就會恢復原樣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果事情真的這麼簡單就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛基他們的鑰匙還是沒有任何反應
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們快撤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 原來你有在啊 灰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要一臉颯爽地跟我裝傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小露
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 蛇夫座怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種傢伙不值一提
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱也很活躍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黃道十二門怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然沒有看到他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 全部都成功強制關門了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…星靈們還是沒有復原
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放棄 還沒有結束不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 總會有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:15.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來整理一下情報比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都來想想辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前 得想辦法從這裏逃出去才是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是某種叫聲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 這樣下去很糟糕啊 要崩壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是剛剛鬧得太厲害了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰啊 把這裏破壞得這麼徹底
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道是哪個不知道手下留情的傢伙弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是在說我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:44.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說這些了 快點逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這要怎麼逃出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得來的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是利用鑰匙上的魔力才…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…難道是星靈王的咆哮？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像他還健在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 不如說比以前更強烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自由儀式·選擇的阻止…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒能趕上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是…不是露西的星靈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍洛洛奇姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話 星靈界會消失的 請幫幫我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是 星靈服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠讓人類在星靈界自由活動的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會去的 一定會去救大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請等一下 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星靈界和這邊世界的時間流速是不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能讓公主你去那種世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使能回來 這裏已經不知道是何時了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有這個覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有夥伴一起去呢 不會有什麼事的 你別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為我聽到了這個聲音 所以我才必須要去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要還能聽見這個咆哮聲 我的贖罪就還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是說這說那的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 只有前進了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是純爺們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間怎樣都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛基他們正遭受危機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以一定要去 僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 露西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算回來的時候已是百年之後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和同伴們一起的話我也不會害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:48.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱比亞只要和灰大人在一起 回到百年前都沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七年的空白 我們也努力戰鬥過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管什麼時代 只要可以大鬧就不是問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗莎娜也會理解我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙也是堅強的男子漢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和其他人一起的話 一定能挺過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好煩惱該不該吐個槽…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再過不久 這個星靈·精神就會被星靈王吸收
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上星靈服 大家就可以去到星靈界了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是公主的盾 是公主的劍 請讓我跟您一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等著我啊 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在就去 可別嚇得逃跑啊 鬍子老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏就是…星靈界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好強的風
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和之前來的時候完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不抓住什麼簡直會被吹飛的說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露西大人…啊呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍洛洛奇姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個傻大個是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 難道那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,純爺們兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是…星靈王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樣子有點可怕啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…才不是我所認識的星靈王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日蝕星靈王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 應該說是星靈獸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像頭一樣的部分的周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有鬍子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,槽點是這個嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 星球上顯示著星靈們的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為被囚禁了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛基
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 我現在就來救你們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸引停止了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 是吸收了黃道十二門 一下子撐到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒完呢 總之狠狠地教訓一下這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏說的對 現在不是哀嘆的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰擊之槌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水流斬破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 完全沒有效果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還遠遠沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單獨攻擊是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌握時機 一起攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獸魂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡片魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.81,0:13:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,固體文字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(834,710)}雷鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(427,710)}子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰加農炮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水流烈鞭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天龍的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鐵龍的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火龍的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是怎麼回事 攻擊完全沒有效果的說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼要來了 大家小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 注意點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是揮了揮手臂就這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:54.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,落地失敗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家別分心 繼續上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:14:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有什麼突破口才對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔細看看他的行動 應該能看到…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可受不了再被胳膊揮飛 先瞄準胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 灰大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱比亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灰…大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？什麼情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱比亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成星座了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 和把洛基他們強制關門時是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣才能恢復原狀…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒那傢伙也許就能復原了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在也沒別的辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能賭在這上面了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伽吉魯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾比
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 總是多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天龍的咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…夏露露
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 得注意不要被那光打中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然將夏露露…混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們上 哈比
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 這次是地圖炮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能隨便靠近了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿魯卡迪歐斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主 趁現在找個藏身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 我現在就過去大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 怎麼樣你才滿意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不原諒你的說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算做什麼啊夏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還用問 用這個揍飛他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還帶這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火龍…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 不能因憤怒迷失心智 否則連你也會被變成星座的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:17:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要躲開就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰凝…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 怎麼辦才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鐵龍棍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 都分不清是軟是硬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管他手感怎麼樣 打趴他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 乾站著也不是辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之想要黃道十二門和變成星座的大家恢復原樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就必須得阻止那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 給我差不多一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 注意那個黑的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心就會被吸進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要太靠前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱們來搞定這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我也一定能幫得上忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我懂了 別勉強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏才是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鐵龍劍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口氣把你變成刺身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好險…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 真是麻煩的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我摔倒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈比 上面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面？這傢伙的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 你準備怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還用問 要揍當然從臉揍起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我醒過來 臭鬍子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好煩人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和洛基戰鬥時流過來的那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別剛吸進去就吐出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星靈獸的…咆哮…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點東西算什麼 鐵龍的咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 這什麼威力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然這麼強大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 魔力消耗太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 能動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能動 就還能站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能站起來 就還能戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有洛基的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那傢伙的咆哮中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定沒錯 洛基他們還在那傢伙身體裏面活著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.26,0:21:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們上哈比
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他打算幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太 太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:22:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MAX速度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.88,0:22:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從外面不行就從裏面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面交給我們 裏面隨你折騰 火龍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 夏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.23,0:22:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也盡力而為！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.06,0:22:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,555)}好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.58,0:24:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算是進到星靈王的身體裏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.08,0:24:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這裏到底是哪裏 簡直就像宇宙一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洛基他們真的被吞噬到這裏面來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.88,0:24:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 雖然不見人 但是能聞到味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.67,0:24:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們一定還在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.26,0:24:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須得救他們才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.67,0:24:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是為了相信咱們而在外面努力戰鬥的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.01,0:24:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 那是自然
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.01,0:24:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣 讓我們來了結這場戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.24,0:24:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回
